  "description": "This dataset comprises EEG recordings from 24 healthy participants performing a multisensory detection task designed to investigate the dynamics of neural activity during selective attention and sensory processing. Participants detected audiovisual targets embedded in simultaneous noise, enabling investigation of modality-specific attention mechanisms and their relationship to electrophysiological spectral properties.",
